well as risk adjusted basis with a focus on delivering long term appreciation and potentially annual cash flow the fund will purchase commercial buildings that the general partner believes will yield at least an  annualized return based on the potential leases and for cash flow and appreciation pcip will also invest in companies where the return has a potential yield of at least  the fund is targeting investment returns to investors of  per annum this return includes both ongoing cash flow from operations as well as appreciation and amortization of debt it is expressed net of any general partner related fees but before any income taxes to be paid by the investors the majority of the fund’s target return is based on the ability to purchase property below market however no assurances can be given that pcip’s target yields appreciation rates or costs as described in this memorandum will be attained request access to our private placement memorandum study sacramento region’s pot economy could soar with legalization — read the article — cannabis real estate investing qa with bill gottlieb and jake schrader of articulated investors — read the article — commercial real estate opportunities in the emerging cannabis industry — read the article — how marijuana became a real estate play the marijuana index releases investor survey  read the article — previousnext platinum capital investment partners lp c offering platform company management team the company is currently managed by seasoned business and sector professionals dedicated to the success of the company and efficient execution of its planned operations platinum capital partners gp llc general partner the general partner is platinum capital partners gp llc a california limited liability company the “general partner” dave walton tom yarak and tom sheridan are its members and its managers the principal office of platinum capital investment partners lp is located at  fallsbrook ct suite  granite bay california  tel   fax 